{"tid":1675521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地府只能收美金？中国新法令 地府冥鈔禁印人民幣圖樣","createTime":"2019-10-26T03:02:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T04:24:15.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ca4c70c62ff2b366ae6e07d98edf98184a2ad6c5","tid":1675521,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T03:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpcrs5AY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpcrs5AY.jpg&h=68ecf6de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（法新社資料照）<br />\n<br />\n中共為了「保護人民幣信譽」，由中國人民銀行（中國央行）昨（25日）公布《人民幣圖樣使用管理辦法》，禁止使用在祭祀用品等物品。<br />\n<br />\n根據中媒《中國新聞網》報導，中共為了加強規範人民幣圖樣使用行為，達成「維護人民幣信譽」和「流通秩序」目的，中國央行發布新法令《人民幣圖樣使用管理辦法》，並自11月15日起實施。<br />\n<br />\n早在今年3月，中國央行就針對人民幣圖樣管制規定向人民公開徵求意見，隨後擬定公布新法，禁止在祭祀用品、生活消耗品、票劵等物品上使用人民幣圖樣，該法更詳細規定人民幣圖樣中的人物頭像、國徽須保持原有比例，確保不變形、失真及破壞等，若有違法行為將毀損該人民幣圖樣，並沒收違法所得，再處人民幣5萬元（約新台幣21.6萬元）以下罰款。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2957990\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2957990&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtNxD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=db856442\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2957990&h=0d668084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2957990</a>"},{"pid":"748c36d2782e3d1369752eb9ab4723bcce9fe5e3","tid":1675521,"uid":301929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T03:03:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vW2nV3L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvW2nV3L.png&h=6943bd03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de87e97dfcefcd6938ab34f505beed48e264bad9","tid":1675521,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T03:03:23.000Z","msg":"笑4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla